                                                                                                                                Time picker

                                                                                                                                Partially stable

                                                                                                                                The time picker component lets our users pick either a time or duration.

                                                                                                                                Trait: Adjustable

                                                                                                                                Label: 40 minute

                                                                                                                                Value: 00, 05, 10, 15, 20, 25, 30, 35, 40, 45, 50, 55

                                                                                                                                Trait: Adjustable

                                                                                                                                Hint: Swipe up or down to adjust value

                                                                                                                                Label: PM

                                                                                                                                Value: AM, PM

                                                                                                                                Trait: Adjustable

                                                                                                                                Hint: Swipe up or down to adjust value
